    "description": "Dungeon of Destiny is a roguelite adventure where you get personality traits and combine them to get classes, abilities and bonuses.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2403110/extras/920c7e6fa068f940635117766cca675a.poster.avif?t=1730473574\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2403110/extras/920c7e6fa068f940635117766cca675a.webm?t=1730473574\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2403110/extras/920c7e6fa068f940635117766cca675a.mp4?t=1730473574\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >1. Choose personality traits as you go forth</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2403110/extras/7ac47a50eac2487310da36585e70ac55.poster.avif?t=1730473574\" width=600 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2403110/extras/7ac47a50eac2487310da36585e70ac55.webm?t=1730473574\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2403110/extras/7ac47a50eac2487310da36585e70ac55.mp4?t=1730473574\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Do you feel smart or strong today? Kind or wicked?<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >2. Combine traits into other traits, classes and something even more complex</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2403110/extras/8041654e294f0fd2f3bc618f44f7d6d9.poster.avif?t=1730473574\" width=600 height=310 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2403110/extras/8041654e294f0fd2f3bc618f44f7d6d9.webm?t=1730473574\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2403110/extras/8041654e294f0fd2f3bc618f44f7d6d9.mp4?t=1730473574\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >3. Fight and explore the rich and peculiar world</h2>Visit strange places, meet strange creatures, choose how you deal with them. Not everyone needs to be your enemy, and the personality you’ve built so far may highly affect your future decisions!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >4. Your looks, fighting style and personality are shaped with every pick</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2403110/extras/54b446259d84068303eb426b18b4c6a8.poster.avif?t=1730473574\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2403110/extras/54b446259d84068303eb426b18b4c6a8.webm?t=1730473574\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2403110/extras/54b446259d84068303eb426b18b4c6a8.mp4?t=1730473574\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Stubborn paladin? Arrogant wizard? Outgoing heretic? You can be all of that - and even all of that at once!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >5. Explore <strong>over 100 traits and classes</strong></h2>Find incredible synergies to beat cunning enemies. Plan your strategy to get to the core of the crazy Dungeon and determine its and your own fate!",
